## Data Preprocessing Workflow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Read CSV File] --> B[Convert Date Column to Datetime]
    B --> C[Sort Data by Date]
    C --> D[Split Input (X) and Output (y)]
    D --> E[Check Missing Values]
    E --> F[Fill Small Gaps with Linear Interpolation]
    F --> G[Fill Large Gaps with Monthly Mean]
    G --> H[Redefine X and y]
    H --> I[Print First 5 Rows of X]
    H --> J[Print First 5 Rows of y]
    H --> K[Print First 20 Rows of Dataset]
